--Armarine Sentinel of Tears
local s,id,o = GetID()
function s.initial_effect(c)
	--During the Main or Battle Phase, when your opponent activates a card or effect while this card is in your hand or field (Quick Effect): You can destroy 1 "Armarine" monster in your hand, also, the activated effect becomes "Your opponent destroys 1 Monster Card they control or in their hand". You can only use this effect of "Armarine Sentinel of Tears" once per turn. If this card battles a monster, neither can be destroyed by that battle. If this card is destroyed by card effect: Until the end of the next turn, the Synchro Summon of your "Armarine" monsters cannot be negated, also your opponent cannot activate cards or effects if an "Armarine" monster is Synchro Summoned.
	end
